<div><head>襄陽記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.2">黃承彥者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.3">高爽闓朗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.4">為沔南名士。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.5">謂諸葛孔明曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.6">「聞君擇婦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.7">某有醜女，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.8">黃頭黑色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.9">而才堪相配。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.10">孔明許，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.11">即載送之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.12">時人以為笑。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.13">樂里為之諺曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.14">「莫作孔明擇婦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1323_CHANT_001-1a.15">正得阿承醜女。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
